Package com.softwareag.natural.mapconverter

Contains data and utility classes and interfaces.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAreaHeaderHandler
    Interface to be implemented by area header handlers is to identify grid headers from the extended map extract.
    IConversionListener
    Listeners to the map conversion must implement this interface.
    IExtendedIfField
    Interface implemented by extended IfField object.
    IMapxmlTransformer
    You can apply an own class implementing this interface to the rules file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComplexTemplate
    Template for complex controls.
    ConvUtil
    Provides helper functions to convert items using templates: Helper functions to access properties/variables which are common to all input items. Helper functions to serialize template tags and attributes.
    MapConverterMain
    MapConverter command line utility.
    MapxmlPage
    Holds the contents of a mapxml file in a convenient form for further processing.
    NameUtil
    Utility class for handling map conversion naming conventionions.
    TemplateTag
    A TemplageTag object describes an XML element of a mapconversion template in a form which is convenient for processing within a corresponding converter.

Package com.softwareag.natural.mapconverter Description

Contains data and utility classes and interfaces.

Data and Utility Classes and Interfaces

This package contains data and utility classes which can be used to implement custom Map Converter extensions.
